## Architecture Overview

```mermaid
graph TD
    subgraph "UI Layer"
        CM[CallModal.tsx]
        CH[ChatHeader.tsx]
    end
    
    subgraph "State Layer"
        CS[call.store.ts<br/>Zustand 15-state machine]
    end

    subgraph "Engine Layer"
        WE[webrtc.engine.ts<br/>RTCPeerConnection abstraction]
    end

    subgraph "Signaling Layer"
        SA[signaling.adapter.ts<br/>WebSocket dispatch]
        SS[socket.service.ts<br/>Socket.IO transport]
    end

    subgraph "API Layer"
        CA[callApi.ts<br/>REST endpoints]
    end

    CH -->|initiateCall| CC
    CM -->|read state| CS
    CM -->|actions| CC
    CC[CallContext.tsx<br/>Orchestrator] --> CS
    CC --> WE
    CC --> SA
    SA --> SS
    CA -->|TURN, history| Backend
```

