## 15-State Call Machine (Frontend)

```mermaid
stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> IDLE
    IDLE --> INITIATING: initiateCall()
    IDLE --> INCOMING: call:signal CALL_INCOMING
    
    INITIATING --> RINGING: call:initiated
    RINGING --> ACCEPTED: call:accepted
    RINGING --> ENDED: cancel
    
    INCOMING --> ACCEPTED: acceptCall()
    INCOMING --> REJECTED: rejectCall()
    
    ACCEPTED --> CONNECTING: media acquired
    CONNECTING --> ICE_NEGOTIATION: SDP exchange
    
    ICE_NEGOTIATION --> AUDIO_CONNECTED: ICE succeeded (audio)
    ICE_NEGOTIATION --> VIDEO_CONNECTED: ICE succeeded (video)
    
    AUDIO_CONNECTED --> VIDEO_UPGRADING: requestVideoUpgrade()
    VIDEO_UPGRADING --> VIDEO_CONNECTED: upgrade complete
    VIDEO_UPGRADING --> AUDIO_CONNECTED: upgrade rejected/timeout
    
    VIDEO_CONNECTED --> AUDIO_CONNECTED: downgradeToAudio()
    
    AUDIO_CONNECTED --> DEGRADED: quality drop
    VIDEO_CONNECTED --> DEGRADED: quality drop
    DEGRADED --> AUDIO_CONNECTED: quality restored
    DEGRADED --> VIDEO_CONNECTED: quality restored
    
    AUDIO_CONNECTED --> RECONNECTING: ICE disconnected
    VIDEO_CONNECTED --> RECONNECTING: ICE disconnected
    RECONNECTING --> AUDIO_CONNECTED: ICE restarted
    RECONNECTING --> FAILED: timeout
    
    AUDIO_CONNECTED --> ENDED: endCall()
    VIDEO_CONNECTED --> ENDED: endCall()
    FAILED --> IDLE: reset
    ENDED --> IDLE: reset
```

---

## Call Lifecycle Sequence

### Outgoing Audio Call
```
Caller                    Server                    Receiver
  |                         |                         |
  |--- call:initiate ------>|                         |
  |<-- call:initiated ------|                         |
  |    (status: RINGING)    |--- call:signal -------->|
  |                         |    CALL_INCOMING        |
  |                         |                         |
  |                         |<-- call:accept ---------|
  |<-- call:accepted -------|                         |
  |    (status: CONNECTING) |                         |
  |                         |                         |
  |--- webrtc:offer ------->|--- webrtc:offer ------->|
  |    (createOffer)        |                         |
  |                         |<-- webrtc:answer -------|
  |<-- webrtc:answer -------|    (createAnswer)       |
  |    (setRemoteDesc)      |                         |
  |                         |                         |
  |<========= ICE Candidates (trickle) =============>|
  |                         |                         |
  |    ICE: connected       |    ICE: connected       |
  |    AUDIO_CONNECTED      |    AUDIO_CONNECTED      |
  |--- call:connected ----->|                         |
  |                         |                         |
  |<===== P2P SRTP Audio (direct or via TURN) ======>|
```

### Mid-Call Voice → Video Upgrade
```
User A                     Server                    User B
  |                          |                          |
  |  AUDIO_CONNECTED         |         AUDIO_CONNECTED  |
  |                          |                          |
  |--- call:upgrade-request->|                          |
  |    VIDEO_UPGRADING       |--- VIDEO_UPGRADE_REQ --->|
  |                          |       VIDEO_UPGRADING    |
  |                          |                          |
  |                          |<-- call:upgrade-accept --|
  |<-- VIDEO_UPGRADE_ACCEPT--|                          |
  |                          |                          |
  |  addVideoTrack()         |      addVideoTrack()     |
  |  createOffer() (w/video) |                          |
  |--- webrtc:offer -------->|--- webrtc:offer -------->|
  |                          |<-- webrtc:answer --------|
  |<-- webrtc:answer --------|                          |
  |                          |                          |
  |--- call:upgrade-complete>|                          |
  |    VIDEO_CONNECTED       |       VIDEO_CONNECTED    |
  |                          |                          |
  |<=== P2P SRTP Audio + Video (direct or TURN) =====>|
```

